							msg &lt;You had over %moneyi% gold and receive %num% #shopitem#&#40;s&#41;&#46; |crNOTE&#58; NOT FINISHED!!!|cb to do&#58; add to inventory&#46;&#46;&#46;&gt; &#125; &#125; 
						else msg &lt;&quot;Fine&#46;&#46;&#46;&quot;&gt; &#125; &#125; 
